Mechanisms exist to obtain consent from data subjects to opt-in for the following Personal Data (PD) actions:
(1) Collecting;
(2) Receiving; 
(3) Processing;
(4) Storing;
(5) Transmitting:
(6) Sharing; and/or
(7) Updating.

