(5) Transmitting:
(6) Sharing; and/or
(7) Updating?

controls.description:
Mechanisms exist to ensure that Personal Data (PD) collection methods are:
(1) In accordance with applicable statutory and/or regulatory requirements;
(2) Appropriate for the circumstances of the data subject;
(3) Unambiguous; and
(4) Secure.

