controls.description:
Mechanisms exist to receive and process data controller communications pertaining to:
(1) Receiving and responding to data subject requests;
(2) Updating/correcting Personal Data (PD); 
(3) Accounting for disclosures of PD; and
(4) Accounting for PD that is stored, processed and/or transmitted on behalf of the data controller.

